description:
Bobby pulled off a surprise graduation ceremony for his girlfriend over the weekend and a surprise trip! Check out the pictures on his Instagram @mrbobbybones. We draft our favorite canned foods in our draft today. Plus, Amy’s husband debuts a new segment on the show called “The Lawn Minute”!
